					<summary>How long does the certification process take?</summary>
					<p>The average processing time is 10 business days from submission of a complete application. Complex cases may require additional review time.</p>
				</details>

				<details class="faq-item">
					<summary>What are the prerequisites for applying?</summary>
					<p>Applicants must have an active ORCiD identifier, be affiliated with a research institution, and complete the required security training modules.</p>
				</details>

				<details class="faq-item">
					<summary>How long is the certification valid?</summary>
					<p>CSR certification is valid for 3 years from the date of issuance, with annual attestation requirements to maintain active status.</p>
				</details>

				<details class="faq-item">
